### ============================================================
### Request Signature (HMAC-SHA256) — @SignatureRequired demo
### ============================================================
### Backed by: src/main/java/.../security/RequestSignatureFilter.java
### Binding:   @SignatureRequired
### Secret:    api.signature.secret  (default "change-me-in-production")
###
### ⚠️  IMPORTANT — current state of the codebase:
### The RequestSignatureFilter and the @SignatureRequired binding are
### implemented, but NO resource method currently carries the
### @SignatureRequired annotation. As-is, none of the requests below
### will trigger the filter. To run this demo live, add @SignatureRequired
### to a method (e.g. SessionResourceV1.createSession) and rebuild.
###
### Computing the signature for the requests below:
###   echo -n '<exact-body>' | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac 'change-me-in-production' -hex
### Then paste the hex digest into the X-Signature header.
### ============================================================


### Demo 1 — Missing X-Signature header → 401 "Missing X-Signature header"
### (only fires once @SignatureRequired is applied to this endpoint)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_organizer}}

{"title":"Signed payload","abstract":"Test","level":"BEGINNER","speakerId":"spk-duke","startTime":"2026-10-16T11:00:00","durationMinutes":50}


### Demo 2 — Wrong signature → 401 "Invalid request signature"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_organizer}}
X-Signature: deadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeefdeadbeef

{"title":"Signed payload","abstract":"Test","level":"BEGINNER","speakerId":"spk-duke","startTime":"2026-10-16T11:00:00","durationMinutes":50}


### Demo 3 — Valid signature → 201 Created
### Recompute the digest if you change a single byte of the body!
###   body='{"title":"Signed payload","abstract":"Test","level":"BEGINNER","speakerId":"spk-duke","startTime":"2026-10-16T11:00:00","durationMinutes":50}'
###   echo -n "$body" | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac 'change-me-in-production' -hex
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_organizer}}
X-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_HEX_DIGEST_FROM_OPENSSL

{"title":"Signed payload","abstract":"Test","level":"BEGINNER","speakerId":"spk-duke","startTime":"2026-10-16T11:00:00","durationMinutes":50}

